name: Jack Sam
description: I am an optimistic and kind man. All my friends say that I am reliable and attentive. I value each day of my life. I am a family-oriented and sociable.I am patience , I never argue. I spend much time with my friends. I enjoy many things. I adore reading. I prefer fiction and men’s novels. I like to watch a good movie and to listen to romantic music. I am fond of bead-work. I like all outdoor and water activities
